00:08:13,876 --> 00:08:16,128
They're gonna kill him.

40
00:08:23,969 --> 00:08:26,055
Jean? You OK?

41
00:08:26,138 --> 00:08:29,015
Yeah. Yeah, I'm fine.

42
00:08:29,099 --> 00:08:32,018
It's just uh... just a headache.

43
00:08:34,104 --> 00:08:36,564
It's not just a headache, is it?

44
00:08:36,648 --> 00:08:40,485
Listen, uh, I wasn't really sure how to say this,
but you know ever since Liberty Island you've been...

45
00:08:40,568 --> 00:08:43,405
- Scott.
- You've been different.

46
00:08:44,531 --> 00:08:48,284
My telepathy's been off lately.
I can't focus. I can hear everything.

47
00:08:48,368 --> 00:08:53,831
